《愤怒》——给我力量去改变我不能改变的情况

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appwV4REAUO9158/v_5cd14f2413287_wbw772ye

<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">-01-</span></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">一个半月前，湖南沅江一个12岁的孩子持刀杀了自己的母亲。原因是男孩觉得母亲干涉太多，而母亲认为男孩不服从管教。他们起先是争执，而后争吵越来越激烈，男孩冲进厨房，拿出菜刀，对着母亲疯狂地砍了20多刀，其母当场死亡。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/12380600_1557220080.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6gr9gg6hqmbu1hfar0hxg7map4iamooiazsji0xvaykibwgpobq08o8dhq/640"/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;一次情绪的失控让一个家庭瞬间支离破碎。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">男孩被退学，被同乡赶出老家，毕竟谁也不想和“杀人犯”做同学、做邻居。<span style="font-weight: bolder;">一次情绪的爆发，断了男孩有无尽可能的未来，而他再也没有了那个生他养他的母亲。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">-02-</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">如果说情绪失控只是偶然中的偶然，那么一次简单的情绪的爆发的后果会怎样？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">知乎有一篇万赞回答，讲了一个故事。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">答主小时候不小心把家门钥匙弄丢，翻箱倒柜找了好几次都没找到，只好和父亲说了这件事。结果父亲大发雷霆，把他骂个狗血淋头，让他站在楼道里罚站。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">楼道是感应灯，所以没过几秒他就要跺个脚，因为黑黑的楼道真的很吓人。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">而门里又传来一阵咆哮“<span style="font-weight: bolder;">罚站还不老实，你想干啥？</span>”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">吓得他站在漆黑的楼道里一动不动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: