nt, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">课程2：</span></span><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">《无力：距离自信你还差几步？》</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">1、为什么你不能站出来说<span style="font-weight: bolder;">“我可以”</span>？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">2、如何做一个<span style="font-weight: bolder;">充满自信和勇气</span>的人？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; te