YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/12380600_1557220080.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6gr9gg6hqmbu1hfar0hxg7map4iamooiazsji0xvaykibwgpobq08o8dhq/640"/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;一次情绪的失控让一个家庭瞬间支离破碎。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">男孩被退学，被同乡赶出老家，毕竟谁也不想和“杀人犯”做同学、做邻居。<span style="font-weight: bolder;">一次情绪的爆发，断了男孩有无尽可能的未来，而他再也没有了那个生他养他的母亲。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">-02-</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">如果说情绪失控只是偶然中的偶然，那么一次简单的情绪的爆发的后果会怎样？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">知乎有一篇万赞回答，讲了一个故事。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">答主小时候不小心把家门钥匙弄丢，翻箱倒柜找了好几次都没找到，只好和父亲说了这件事。结果父亲大发雷霆，把他骂个狗血淋头，让他站在楼道里罚站。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">楼道是感应灯，所以没过几秒他就要跺个脚，因为黑黑的楼道真的很吓人。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">而门里又传来一阵咆哮“<span style="font-weight: bolder;">罚站还不老实，你想干啥？</span>”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">吓得他站在漆黑的楼道里一动不动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/51190700_1557220080.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6anegdg6ibqq6gvcrzklksrbrplwmlsjpjdnhnwhora2i90unticbgk4a/640"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">若干年后，他父亲在酒桌上和同事们说，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><br/></span></span></p><blockquote style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">“别的孩子回家跟父母有说不完的话，我这儿子就喜欢把自己一个人闷在屋里。”</span></span></p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">只是一次情绪爆发，就能影响孩子一生的性格和父子关系。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">-03-</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">每个人都自以为是情绪的主人，但当它们真正来临是，绝大多数人都会沦为情绪的奴隶，任它们破坏亲密关系、亲子关系，还容易被憋出内伤。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">你最近一次发火是什么时候？</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">是今天早上孩子不写作业的催促皱眉？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">还是昨天晚上伴侣回家太晚了的抱怨？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">还是在公司里对员工工作成果的呵斥？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">还是自己一个人坐在床脚的生闷气？</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/69476800_1557220080.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz64xnompgfpevsopgj7xkvibbdbk0icje2ev4xdukxt4lxl5vbn99fdthg/640"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">如果你经常控制不住地对身边亲人发脾气，或者情绪化严重，推荐您华人NLP大师李中莹老师的学问。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">李中莹老师一向相信情绪对人的作用和意义远超过传统和现代人所理解的，他发现NLP没有研究情绪、而科学或心理学的领域里，对这方面的研究也是极少(他认为情绪是人类最重要而认识最少的东西)。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">从1995年起，他本着「实用主义者」的心态，认真地研究情绪，并且发展出来甚多的重要概念和技巧。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">他认为，</span></span></span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">人生中出现的各种负面情绪，除了一种“恨”之外，都有其正面的价值和意义，不是给我们一些力量，就是指引我们找寻更好的方向，有一些甚至两者俱备。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如，愤怒是给我们力量去改变一个不能接受的情况。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">电影中和社会罪案里的主角警告对方不要激怒他，否则“什么事情都做得出来”，便是最好的例证。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">今天的社会里充满内心力量不足的人，他们往往需要生活在愤怒里，以维持更多的力量去面对人生的状态。这就像一个人在冬天里燃烧自己的腿去取暖，只会使问题越来越严重。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">比如，委屈是小孩子对父母的情结投射在其他人事物身上。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">委屈的意思是：“你没有给我你应该给我的。”</span></span><span style="font-size: 15px;">感到委屈的人把自己放在低位，把对方放在高位，操控着自己。在这个世界上只有小孩子会觉得什么都是他该得到的，而且不管要多少、什么时候要，父母都有责任满足他。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">心理成熟的人知道：满足自己的需要是自己的责任，对方没有一定的责任要给我什么；并且，这里得不到，我可以去别的地方拿到。</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><img style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/31987100_1557220113.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6rg7f7qs2yxmnfp7ajhs7yibktcqhmiy3nrphktdcrqsnu58k93xp5ka/640"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span><br/><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">他还研究出了很多情绪处理的方法，比如<span style="font-weight: bolder;">呼吸放松法、挂钩法、现场抽离法、逐步抽离法、意义储留心中法</span>等，为自己处理情绪的方法，还有处理他人情绪的<span style="font-weight: bolder;">EQ型处理法</span>。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">这些方法，让许多学员获益匪浅。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;<img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/49874700_1557220081.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6ibb8r26l4azrxuapiagtfj06colaaumjocqrgz3icotvcf711zpcz9qug/640"/></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/88819700_1557220081.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6mr9drm8uicuau7iatihz58ibpmjdt8apnecjx36qe15icgyazqpezawzyg/640"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/27636900_1557220082.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6czickeufkf8wusmz30rdxu6zorvaiaz3hql9vdwt9wic8lclpm7n3op9q/640"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">他对情绪的研究不仅限于此，上面的方法可以让一个人快速消解情绪，</span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">但真正让一个人产生情绪的并非是事件本身，而是事件背后的信念价值观。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appwoRl918Q2976/image/ueditor/40506600_1557220082.cn/mmbiz_png/icyib0db68l4qlkccmwiasidrc973utpcz6f6gt3g6hpsnex719oyeqxcogsyrws5fmwbj3nsa8dgieh7bqvb0kicw/640"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">如果把人比作工厂里的机器，那么情绪就是机器的警示灯。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">机器出了故障，警示灯亮了，维修员会走过来关掉警示灯，打开机箱，开始逐一排查故障点，找到故障点后修好，再让机器正常运作。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">那么人呢？</span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">有了情绪之后，通常的做法就是压抑、逃避、发泄和自省。不会去想情绪背后的“故障点”是什么，只是用各种做法关掉了“警示灯”，就认为已经修好了。这样只会留下更大的隐患。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">那么，如何找到情绪背后的信念价值观并做出改变呢？</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">李中莹老师将挑选出常见的如<span style="font-weight: bolder;">愤怒、压力、抑郁</span>等几种情绪，<span style="font-weight: bolder;">分专题来讲述每一种情绪产生的可能性原因，并配以实际案例答疑</span>，另外还有设有<span style="font-weight: bolder;">个案演示技巧</span>，让每个人都能轻松学习。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; f