<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 169, 0);">-01-</span></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">一个半月前，湖南沅江一个12岁的孩子持刀杀了自己的母亲。原因是男孩觉得母亲干涉太多，而母亲认为男孩不服从管教。他们起先是争执，而后争吵越来越激烈，男孩冲进厨房，拿出菜刀，对着母亲疯狂地砍了20多刀，其母当场死亡。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft 