stem-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">楼道是感应灯，所以没过几秒他就要跺个脚，因为黑黑的楼道真的很吓人。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">而门里又传来一阵咆哮“<span style="font-weight: bolder;">罚站还不老实，你想干啥？</span>”</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">吓得他站在漆黑的楼道里一动不动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: